    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[520ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[750ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>- this is your<strong> coconut stock</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>to the pan and bring to the boil</p>",
